data.title: 85 Mckenzie Cres, Piers Island Home For Sale 685000
data.meta_description: Carly Carey would love to show you 85 Mckenzie Cres. Once in a lifetime opportunity to own this fabulous Piers Island custom waterfront home with private dock & cement retaining wall! Idyllic oceanfront living is only 5 min. from Swartz Bay by shuttle or your own boat. This thoughtful 3 bedroom, den home was built with the whole family in mind & offers a spectacular master with private deck & ensuite with double sinks and Jacuzzie tub. Huge country kitchen overlooking almost 1000SF of multilevel decks! Spectacular unrivalled waterfront views to the islands. Extras include metal roof, solid oak flooring in LR, french doors to deck areas, wood stove, walk in pantry, large laundry room, inside workshop room w/2 pc bath & separate entrance.Large wired shop could be a bunky as well!
